          "updatedAt": "2024-12-08T20:54:25Z",
          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 20,
              "body": "I would word this as \"to prevent fragmentation\" rather than \"to receive errors\", since fragmentation is the hazard we're specifically seeking to avoid.\r\n\r\n> I am not sure one should set it on v4.\r\n\r\nLinux doesn't have an IPv4 DONTFRAG, afaict.",
              "createdAt": "2024-12-08T20:54:25Z",
              "updatedAt": "2024-12-08T20:54:25Z"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "id": "PRR_kwDONMXNnM6UQM3X",
          "commit": {
            "abbreviatedOid": "d4c1bf0"
