          "state": "COMMENTED",
          "body": "",
          "createdAt": "2024-12-16T11:36:51Z",
          "updatedAt": "2024-12-16T11:36:51Z",
          "comments": [
            {
              "originalPosition": 17,
              "body": "My initial version described the error reporting of `IPV6_DONTFRAG` only. @Ralith suggested the \"prevent [local] fragmentation\" in https://github.com/marten-seemann/draft-seemann-tsvwg-udp-fragmentation/pull/14#discussion_r1875042458.",
              "createdAt": "2024-12-16T11:36:51Z",
