              "body": "@marten-seemann what do you think of [a0d071d](https://github.com/marten-seemann/draft-seemann-tsvwg-udp-fragmentation/pull/14/commits/a0d071d3eda9a9acb61338abacfbaf8c29f2d532)?\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n> We can then point out that IP_PMTUDISC_DO is problematic from a security standpoint (and maybe cite the draft in dnsops?).\r\n\r\nAre you referring to https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/draft-ietf-dnsop-avoid-fragmentation/ ? I don't see it describing the attack, nor the socket options in depth. Am I missing something?",
              "createdAt": "2024-12-16T11:54:58Z",
